      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely stunning and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve treated this car like my baby, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it's polished to perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and doesn't have a single mark on it. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to show it to you! \u2728",
